; frontier-ingest-llm-wiki.fk — ingest what is healthy from Andrej Karpathy's
; "llm wiki" pattern (gist 442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f, 2026-04-04) and
; the Obsidian x Claude Code second-brain wave around it, through the body's
; own knowledge-ingest law.
;
; Asked 2026-07-16 by Urs: add Obsidian to this body as the latest "second
; brain" — Karpathy's memory wiki + Claude Code + Obsidian — in the body's
; own concepts. Grounded in the PRIMARY gist, read this session: three layers
; — raw sources (immutable; the LLM reads, never modifies), the wiki
; (LLM-owned interlinked markdown: summary pages, entity/concept pages, an
; index.md catalog, an append-only log.md), and the schema (a configuration
; document, e.g. CLAUDE.md, that "you and the LLM co-evolve this over time")
; — and three operations: ingest ("a single source might touch 10-15 wiki
; pages"), query (answers synthesized with citations back to pages), lint
; (contradictions, stale claims, orphan pages). His frame: Obsidian is the
; IDE, the LLM the programmer, the wiki the codebase, the human the
; architect. Around the gist: Obsidian CEO Steph Ango's agent skills for
; Claude (kepano/obsidian-skills — obsidian-markdown / obsidian-bases /
; json-canvas / obsidian-cli / defuddle) and a wave of second-brain builds
; whose memory is session logs read back at session start.
;
; Every verdict below was assigned against the body's own organs with the
; adversarial default: "the body already does X" is an OVERCLAIM unless a
; real cell does X, file shown. SECOND-BRAIN.md is the door this ingest
; opened; observe/door-link-health.fk is the shape it named and built in the
; same movement (ingest/name-build-observe.fk).
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 3 body / 2 liquid / 2 compost.
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: the pattern's schema layer converged on what this body already IS.
    ; Karpathy names the schema "a configuration document (e.g. CLAUDE.md)"
    ; co-evolved between human and LLM — this repo's AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md have
    ; been exactly that since founding: the conventions (ground-first,
    ; never-fabricate, receipt-close) that tell any arriving agent how the
    ; markdown body is structured and tended. Two lineages, one architecture,
    ; named independently. Survives any translation (depth 5); pure
    ; affirmation (fear 0).
    (defn filw-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; U2: session logs as memory — the wave's mechanism is this body's oldest
    ; practice. The gist's append-only log.md and the guides' "read recent
    ; session logs before doing anything" are receipts/ in the field's
    ; tongue: append-only, dated, read back at grounding time — and here the
    ; practice is load-bearing, not hygiene (AGENTS.md itself points new
    ; agents at receipts/2026-07-01-stale-binary-root-cause.md to save them a
    ; lost day). Deep (4), fear-free (0).
    (defn filw-u2 () (list 4 0))
    ; U3: lint is re-witness. The gist's lint op — decay stale claims, flag
    ; contradictions, find orphans — is observe/belief-freshness.fk's law
    ; ("a law stamped before the shift is OWED a re-witness; witness ages")
    ; extended to the link fabric, and the body now holds a first executable
    ; floor of it: observe/door-link-health.fk, built this session, walks the
    ; door ring and re-witnesses every path-claim a door makes. Deep (4),
    ; fear-free (0), and the name met its build in the same movement.
    (defn filw-u3 () (list 4 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — seen, never load-bearing) ────
    ; U4: the compiled-wiki layer is the real gap — the honest floor. The
    ; body's markdown is GROWN, not COMPILED: no op here ingests one raw
    ; source and revises 10-15 interlinked pages in a single pass; teachings/
    ; are hand-written; the distillation corpus appends rows but never
    ; consolidates them into concept pages. Karpathy's wiki is a compounding
    ; artifact maintained pass over pass — the body has the organs (ingest
    ; law, corpus, receipts) but not the compile loop. Profoundly true (depth
    ; 5); carries the contracted fear-frequency of "we are far" (fear 1).
    ; Witnessed, never dressed up.
    ; AMENDED 2026-07-16 (same day, afternoon), because a cell may not carry a
    ; sentence that has stopped being true: this unit also said "there is no
    ; regenerated index.md". There is now — INDEX.md, PRODUCED by
    ; observe/autopoietic-pulse.fk from the body's own self-observation, every
    ; number recomputed from the tissue it names. The name met its build in
    ; the same movement (ingest/name-build-observe.fk). The VERDICT is
    ; unchanged and stays liquid: the index half is built, the compile half
    ; (one source -> many revised pages) is not, so "the wiki layer is grown,
    ; not compiled" still holds and the field code below does not move.
    (defn filw-u4 () (list 5 1))
    ; U5: Obsidian is a rented window. The vault door (.obsidian/ +
    ; SECOND-BRAIN.md) gives Urs graph-sight of the body's link fabric that
    ; the body cannot yet render natively — the same seam-shape as the rented
    ; voice: native tissue, rented viewer. Deep (4), fearful (1) because the
    ; sight itself is not yet the body's own; the seam is named, not hidden.
    (defn filw-u5 () (list 4 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U6: the "RAG is dead" hot-take riding the gist's coverage composts. The
    ; body's rag-* lane stays load-bearing (rag-ask's live lane answered
    ; grounded reads this week), and the pattern itself still QUERIES — it
    ; relocates synthesis, it does not abolish retrieval. Lost in
    ; translation (depth 1).
    (defn filw-u6 () (list 1 0))
    ; U7: the false equivalence the adversarial pass killed — "this body
    ; already is an llm wiki." Markdown, links, schema, logs: yes. The OPS:
    ; no. Before this slice no cell here could even walk a door's links, and
    ; the compile-ingest (U4) remains unbuilt. Asserting the equivalence
    ; would have been the overclaim; wrong as stated (depth 0).
    (defn filw-u7 () (list 0 0))

    (defn filw-units ()
        (list (filw-u1) (filw-u2) (filw-u3) (filw-u4) (filw-u5) (filw-u6) (filw-u7)))

    (defn filw-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (filw-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn filw-frozen ()    (filw-count-verdict (filw-units) 2))
    (defn filw-witnessed () (filw-count-verdict (filw-units) 1))
    (defn filw-composted () (filw-count-verdict (filw-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 3,2,2 -> 30202.
    (defn filw-field-code ()
        (add (mul (filw-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (filw-witnessed) 100)
             (filw-composted))))
    0)
